: ["nocode", "collaboration", "learning", "creation", "social"], "long_description": "Zoe enables the rapid creation of interactive 3D scenes through a no-code interface and automation. Invite your friends, students, colleagues and clients to collaborate, learn and create together in real-time. \n\nWhat can I create with Zoe?\n\nWith Zoe you can create anything you have in mind. It has been used to host remote workshops, virtual classrooms, project-based-learning activities, meetups, events and create interactive stories, adventure games, and even mini-games for therapy.\n\nOur free version includes templates, creator tools and multiplayer capabilities for up to 3 members. To purchase more collaborators, head over to www.zoe.com.\n\n7 Launch Templates\n8 Environments\n350+ Local Assets\n1M+ Online Assets Through Sketchfab\n3 Projects and 3 Scenes Per Project\nUnlimited Interactions\n\nIf you would like to submit a template you created to be integrated into our next community update, go to zoe.com/templates and fill out the form.\n", "short_description": "For ages 13 and up\nZoe enables the rapid creation of interactive 3D scenes through a no-code interface and automation. Invite your friends, students, colleagues and clients to collaborate, learn and create together in real-time. \nWhat can I create with Zoe?\nZoe has been used to host immersive workshops, virtual classrooms, project-based-learning activities, meetups, events, interactive art, marketing campaigns, and even mini-games for therapy.\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.zoe.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Zoe Immersive", "support_website_url": "https://docs.zoe.com/", "website_url": "https://www.zoe.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1573854509480616"}], "external